1. Introduction
In the previous article, we learned how to use redirectTo and the Wildcard ('**') route.
In this article, we’ll learn how to pass data while navigating between components using:

• Route Parameters

• Query Parameters
Although both are used to pass information in the URL, they work differently.
2. What We Will Build
Press enter or click to view image in full size

We’ll create:

• Student List

• Student Details
We’ll learn:

• Pass student id using Route Parameters

• Pass additional information using Query Parameters
